  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>Frequently asked questions</h2>
    </div>

    <div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
      <div class="card card-flat mb-4">
        <h4>When do I pay the $4,990?</h4>
        <p class="text-muted mb-0">Only when your property successfully sells. If it doesn't sell, you don't pay.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card card-flat mb-4">
        <h4>Are there any hidden fees?</h4>
        <p class="text-muted mb-0">No. $4,990 is the total fee for sellers. Buyers never pay us anything.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card card-flat mb-4">
        <h4>What's included in the seller fee?</h4>
        <p class="text-muted mb-0">Everything: listing creation, buyer matching, offer management, negotiation guidance, contract support, and settlement assistance.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card card-flat mb-4">
        <h4">Do I still need a conveyancer?</h4>
        <p class="text-muted mb-0">Yes â€” you'll need a conveyancer or solicitor for the legal aspects of the sale. We can connect you with trusted professionals if needed.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center mt-12">
      <%= link_to "Get started free", new_user_registration_path, class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

